    <h1>
      LIFE
      </h1>
      <p>
      Life is sweet<br>
        life is bitter<br>
        life has alot to offer<br>
        life is good<br>
        yet life is hard<br>
        Check the books<br>
        and you will find<br>
        life remains<br>
        just the same<br>
        all that changes<br>
        are the people in the game<br>
      </p>
      <i> -Rafihatu Bello (2020)</i>
